# Bitcoin Price Prediction for 2030

This project explores the long-term trajectory of Bitcoin (BTC) using historical data, technical indicators, and time series forecasting models. It aims to estimate Bitcoin‚Äôs potential price by the year 2030 based on trends observed from 2015 to 2025.

---

## üìå Project Overview

- **Asset**: Bitcoin (BTC)
- **Forecast Horizon**: 2025 ‚Üí 2030
- **Data Source**: CoinGecko API (daily OHLCV)
- **Tools Used**: Python, Pandas, Plotly, Prophet, scikit-learn
- **Focus Areas**:
  - Historical price trends and volatility
  - Technical indicators (RSI, MACD, SMA)
  - Time series forecasting (Prophet, ARIMA)
  - Scenario modeling and uncertainty visualization

---

## üß∞ Features

- üìà Fetches and cleans 10 years of BTC price data
- üìä Visualizes historical trends and market cycles
- üß† Applies forecasting models to project future prices
- üßÆ Compares multiple prediction scenarios (conservative, optimistic, speculative)
- üß± Modular code structure for reproducibility
